text: Ilyakshide () is a rural locality (a village) in Bishkurayevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 240 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo, 2 km from Bishkurayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Ilyakshide
